  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fishing mini-game where typing accumulates resources for catches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This adorable little kitten stays on your desktop, keeping you company day and night</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every keystroke during work/study earns ‌<strong>Cat Paws Coins</strong>‌! When you need a break, guide the kitten in a chill fishing game to collect fish of varying rarity & unlock aquatic surprises.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi everyone, we're a tiny development team releasing our first indie game on Steam. Our goal is to bring some relaxation and fun to your workdays. While we originally planned many features like customizable scene layouts, player-created fish, and fish combination mechanics, limited resources and time constraints led us to launch with core gameplay first. We truly appreciate your support! We'll keep working hard to add more engaging content in future updates~~<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/7b90c9d59e90e46cb35a0ad5a7264025.avif?t=1746596028\" width=616 height=72 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/f91938e6962260bd5d732f2f70fbe146.poster.avif?t=1746596028\" width=426 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/f91938e6962260bd5d732f2f70fbe146.webm?t=1746596028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/f91938e6962260bd5d732f2f70fbe146.mp4?t=1746596028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/5bb7d28f88f1406ffae242b62282668a.avif?t=1746596028\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/19cb2b5078411a00cd8618354f443052.poster.avif?t=1746596028\" width=426 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/19cb2b5078411a00cd8618354f443052.webm?t=1746596028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/19cb2b5078411a00cd8618354f443052.mp4?t=1746596028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/2dd18d4fffc5b3d502459ff5dfe723ac.avif?t=1746596028\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fishing mini-game where typing accumulates resources for catches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This adorable little kitten stays on your desktop, keeping you company day and night</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every keystroke during work/study earns ‌<strong>Cat Paws Coins</strong>‌! When you need a break, guide the kitten in a chill fishing game to collect fish of varying rarity & unlock aquatic surprises.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi everyone, we're a tiny development team releasing our first indie game on Steam. Our goal is to bring some relaxation and fun to your workdays. While we originally planned many features like customizable scene layouts, player-created fish, and fish combination mechanics, limited resources and time constraints led us to launch with core gameplay first. We truly appreciate your support! We'll keep working hard to add more engaging content in future updates~~<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/7b90c9d59e90e46cb35a0ad5a7264025.avif?t=1746596028\" width=616 height=72 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/f91938e6962260bd5d732f2f70fbe146.poster.avif?t=1746596028\" width=426 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/f91938e6962260bd5d732f2f70fbe146.webm?t=1746596028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/f91938e6962260bd5d732f2f70fbe146.mp4?t=1746596028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/5bb7d28f88f1406ffae242b62282668a.avif?t=1746596028\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/19cb2b5078411a00cd8618354f443052.poster.avif?t=1746596028\" width=426 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/19cb2b5078411a00cd8618354f443052.webm?t=1746596028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/19cb2b5078411a00cd8618354f443052.mp4?t=1746596028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3642530/extras/2dd18d4fffc5b3d502459ff5dfe723ac.avif?t=1746596028\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
